WEBVTT

00:00:28.935 --> 00:00:31.020
i tona iza ovih rečenica,

00:00:31.020 --> 00:00:33.648
to zaista mogu 
biti komplimenti.

00:00:33.648 --> 00:00:35.260
Ipak, to takođe
mogu biti

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:37.820
zajedljive
i napadne rečenice.

00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:40.906
Ova blaga promena stava
iza rečenica

00:00:40.906 --> 00:00:44.995
otkriva ono što nazivamo 
verbalnom ironijom.

00:00:44.995 --> 00:00:48.570
Kada neko kaže: 
"Kakvo sjajno vreme",

00:00:48.570 --> 00:00:52.126
moguće je da ta osoba
zaista to i misli,

00:00:52.126 --> 00:00:53.259
ako sunce sija,

00:00:53.259 --> 00:00:54.625
ptice pevaju

00:00:54.625 --> 00:00:56.611
i vetar je miran.

00:00:56.611 --> 00:00:58.043
Ali ako je vreme užasno,

00:00:58.043 --> 00:00:59.074
naziru se oblaci,

00:00:59.074 --> 00:01:01.178
a vetar je
pobesnela oluja